{"tid":1688841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］香港人抗爭運動三個新方向？","createTime":"2019-11-02T14:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T15:16:05.000Z","uid":25425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7c0328955ce3f482e8c9aeebba4f851cfdd861","tid":1688841,"uid":25425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"第一：最近風向「屠狗」<br />\n<br />\n個人評論，自己唔願意做唔好推人去做同埋個人後果好嚴重，少人會響應。未到最後一步大家都唔會簡依一步。<br />\n<br />\n第二：全民三罷<br />\n<br />\n成效大就必須要時間夠耐，但係有家庭負擔既人又點去承擔無收入既日子。有搞手整緊公會我十分支持，但係去到組織到行動都要一段既時間。我諗唔少人都等唔切好想立即向政權施壓。<br />\n<br />\n第三：轉換MPF做美股<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vUQ688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vUQ688.jpg&h=a77fef06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個做保險嘅朋友同我講過恒指點解死都唔會跌穿20000點，就係因為偉大既打工仔投揀嘅MPF。依個係一個成效一般容易實行。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以推多啲idea出黎，不過一有共識就文宣推俾全香港人知！"},{"pid":"aff03dc1529ed1289898944a94a2c0ad3c1dda71","tid":1688841,"uid":25425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"94a4b5f213c2ff6094f9b16d1b3670e1016cb410","tid":1688841,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=6e805f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"e539a2b8ce12a48d1b1b9684be35b1ef7279c269","tid":1688841,"uid":25425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:59:22.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"a8349343918b8b79848b5251a52076d9dd780333","tid":1688841,"uid":25425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"想有新既行動"},{"pid":"59127d24629920650b3099287d6f3